==Strategy==
{{Main|Scorpia/Strategies}}
See main article for gear setups and explanation on fight mechanics.

Scorpia drains 2 [[prayer point]]s every time she attempts a melee attack if the player has an overhead prayer on. She will spawn two [[Scorpia's guardian]]s on the ''next'' attack after Scorpia reaches 99 health or lower, even if you splash.

